column2: "Thank you! Thanks to your help, I was able to spread the word of the Aries Knights to everyone."
"Hmm, I just remembered that I was transported to this world before I had a chance to eat lunch..."
"That gives me an idea! I've got another request for you, if you're interested!"
"By the way, I know I've already thanked you, but would you like some wakame stems? They're my favorite snack!"

"I'm sure I had some somewhere around here... Huh? They're gone?!
...Never mind. Thanks again."
